映售價完全按受助者負擔能力出發的重大原則。<br />\n<br />\n係咪on9 架？政府放抽簽時九龍區離島區一樣價<br />\n<br />\n咁一係就九龍區第一輪被人揀曬，新界無人揀<br />\n一係就新界都被人揀曬，推高埋新界啲樓"},{"pid":"bf333591ad01c5c0ac3bcad9ea1f1c2ceab2dfdc","tid":720752,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab7fa34ecc8eb7fc64397cbb69a51feaba10ba45","tid":720752,"uid":71058,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"咩叫參考申請者既入息?<br />\n姐係唔同人買唔同單位就唔同價?<br />\n所有申請者加埋既中位數?<br />\n姐係拉CURVE? <br />\n講到1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接市價打4 , 5 折咪算囉屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"佢又唔想直接折喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣人情同時都要吸盡你購買力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf173ac1a68b3f617413eb3516bbd66513b52ca","tid":720752,"uid":170015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"仲有喎，佢啲入息中位數，供款比率，年期呢三個數係要用番對上一次賣居屋條數<br />\n<br />\n因為政府賣新制居屋都要計左個價先俾市民去入票交表去抽<br />\n<br />\n咁上一次居屋係已經痴線價，咁供款比率，年期一定大架喇，咁可以平幾多呀？？？？？？？？"},{"pid":"1e554d5c0b04d5177cedd1b939d14c2ccf55905c","tid":720752,"uid":144843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"821df38c56455b9a93fff0483b6a8ec50a5c8c45","tid":720752,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"新移民又可以幾千蚊租住九龍區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抽居屋資格都冇既我要貴租新界, 再每日來回三個鐘車去中環返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68027bb31ac8f8d41d3fe8555a899e9870df4a9e","tid":720752,"uid":39326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"781fc5e931b3b8823f5a0c88be694c2bac1d0d54","tid":720752,"uid":36454,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"citedBy":7,"replyTime